 Policy development, planning and implementation which are related
to routine activities such as personnel, organizational changes or
similar administrative functions;

 Activities which deal solely with the functions of programs, such
as program budget proposals, disbursement, transfer or reprogramming
of funds;

 Inventories, research activities and studies, such as resource
inventories and routine data collection when such actions are
clearly limited in context and intensity;

 Repair, replacement of structural components or equipment, or other
routine maintenance of facilities controlled in whole or in part by
ARS;

 Inventories, studies or other such activities that have limited
context and minimal intensity in terms of changes in the
environment;

 Programs, supported in the majority by ARS, which may assist in the
transition of a particular technology from field evaluation stage to
large-scale demonstration or simulated commercial phase;
